<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Generative ZSL on Chen Kai Blog</title><link>https://www.chenk.top/zh/tags/generative-zsl/</link><description>Recent content in Generative ZSL on Chen Kai Blog</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 06 Jun 2025 09:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.chenk.top/zh/tags/generative-zsl/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>迁移学习（七）：零样本学习</title><link>https://www.chenk.top/zh/transfer-learning/07-%E9%9B%B6%E6%A0%B7%E6%9C%AC%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/</link><pubDate>Fri, 06 Jun 2025 09:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.chenk.top/zh/transfer-learning/07-%E9%9B%B6%E6%A0%B7%E6%9C%AC%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/</guid><description>&lt;p>你从没见过斑马。我告诉你，它外形似马，身披黑白相间条纹。下次你在动物园看到斑马时，一眼就能认出来。无需标注数据，也无需微调，仅需一座&lt;strong>语义桥梁&lt;/strong>，将你已知的概念（如马、条纹）与未知类别（如斑马）关联起来。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>